---
import Container from "./Container.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import team1 from "../images/team1.png";
---

<Container>
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-5 my-5">
    <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-powder-blue">OUR FOUNDERS</h3>
    <p class="text-gun-metal-light md:text-xl text-center md:w-3/4">
      Allow us to introduce our founders, Dawn and Naz, Both share a deep
      commitment to offering compassionate and empowering support to young
      people. Their collaboration has resulted in the establishment of an
      outcome-focused supported living accommodation for young people over the
      age of 16.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gun-metal-light md:text-xl text-center md:w-3/4">
      Leveraging their diverse backgrounds in business management and youth
      support, they have developed an innovative approach to supported living.
      Their combined eight years of experience in youth support, infuses Harbour
      Light with both expertise and empathy, fostering a nurturing space where
      every young person can thrive
    </p>
  </div>
  <div
    class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:justify-around items-center space-y-5"
  >
    <div>
      <Image alt="logo" src={team1} loading={"lazy"} />
      <p class="text-powder-blue text-xl mt-6">Nazrawi Solomon</p>
      <p class="text-gun-metal-light">Position #1</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <Image alt="logo" src={team1} loading={"lazy"} />
      <p class="text-powder-blue text-xl mt-6">Nazrawi Solomon</p>
      <p class="text-gun-metal-light">Position #1</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Container>
